Tinodikana kuziva muvengi wedu , asi atidikani kumuthya .
( 1 Johani 2 : 14 ) Kudari tikahwisana naye , iyena anozotitiza .
Ngozvapi zvijito zvo hondo yo kumujimu ?
Zve vabari vangu no shamwari jangu vangandithemba . ”
Asi , mungatova no muviyo jakanakisisa : Mungathembwa , mungajizwa kuti muri phedo na Jehovha zve mungareremejwa ngo vaya vanomuda . ”
Bhande ro cokwadi ( Vonanyi ndima 3 - 5 )
Ndakazoguma pa kutama kujithembazve zve ndaisuruvara maningi . ”
‘ Shamwari ’ jangu jimweni jakatanga kumwa mutombo jinodhakwisa ; vamweni vakatosia kujija .
Zvinosuruvarisa kuvona macinjire akaita upenyu hwavo .
“ Ndinozviceukija ndega kuti ndinotora zina ra Jehovha zve muejo wondhowo ndi njira inoshandisa Sathana kuti andibvisire zina iro .
Pandinokwanisa kuhwa , ndinojizwa ushoni pacangu . ”
Muthavo wo ururami ( Vonanyi ndima 6 - 8 )
Wari , ndinodakara maningi ngo kucumaera ku vadoni vangu . ”
Ngokudaro ndinokwanisa kuvona zvingavabesa .
Pandinonga ndanasiririka , ndinobhuya navo ngo pamusoro po zviro zvingavabesera . ”
Ndinova no cokwadi co kuti ndakaverenga zvese zvakabudiswa kuitira majaha no vasikane .
Ngo njira iyi ndingabesera vadoni vangu ngo kushandisa Bhaibheri kana jw.org . ”
Simiranyi magwada mu soka menyu ( Vonanyi ndima 9 - 11 )
Ngojapi mupasha jimweni jinobwaka ja Sathana ?
Wari , ndinonasirira musongano zve ndinoeja kudavira kaviri kana katutu .
Zvinonesa , asi ndinojizwa ushoni pandinozviita .
Zve hama no hambzaji jinondivangisa maningi .
Nguva jese ndinobva ku musongano ndeciziva kuti Jehovha anodida . ”
Muvhikiro wo rutendo ( Vonanyi ndima 12 - 14 )
Cigoko co ruponeso ( Vonanyi ndima 15 - 18 )
Ndakavona kuti vandhu vanonasa kudakarira pavanovona kuti munoda Bhaibheri kamare zve munoita zvamunokwanisa kuti muvabesere . ”
Banga ro mujimu ( Vonanyi ndima 19 - 20 )
No besero ra Jehovha , tingaramba takavanga pa kuhwisana naye !
